    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "PowerShell 用于自动化任务和配置管理的常用命令的备忘清单，可帮助系统管理员快速参考常用操作。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "辅助命令",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**_PowerShell 的命令遵循动词-名词格式_** 一些常见的动词:"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "| 动词    | 描述                     |\n| ------- | ------------------------ |\n| Get     | 用于检索信息             |\n| Set     | 用于配置或更改设置       |\n| New     | 用于创建新对象实例       |\n| Remove  | 用于删除或移除项目       |\n| Invoke  | 用于执行特定的操作或动作 |\n| Start   | 用于启动进程或操作       |\n| Stop    | 用于停止或终止进程或操作 |\n| Enable  | 用于激活或启用功能       |\n| Disable | 用于停用或禁用功能       |\n| Test    | 用于执行测试或检查       |\n| Update  | 用于更新或刷新数据或配置 |"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "列出可用模块"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-4",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Module --ListAvailable"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-5",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "列出可用的 cmdlet 和函数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-6",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Command -Module ActiveDirectory"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-7",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "列出别名及其对应的 cmdlet 名称"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-8",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Alias | Select-Object Name, Definition"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-9",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "获取帮助"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-10",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Help <cmd>\nGet-Help <cmd> -Examples\nGet-Help -Name Get-Process -Parameter Id"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-11",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Get-Member:** 显示对象的属性和方法"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-12",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Process | Get-Member"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-13",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "对象操作",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Select-Object:** 选择对象的特定属性或自定义其显示"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-14",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Process | Select-Object Name, CPU"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-15",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Where-Object:** 根据指定条件过滤对象"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-16",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Service | Where-Object { $PSItem.Status -eq 'Running' }\n#OR\nGet-Service | ? { $_.Status -eq 'Running' }"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-17",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Measure-Object:** 计算对象属性的统计信息，如总和、平均值和计数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-18",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Process | Measure-Object -Property WorkingSet -Sum"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-19",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**ForEach-Object:** 对集合中的每个对象执行操作（注意：以下命令将为当前目录中的文件/文件夹添加前缀）"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-20",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-ChildItem%20%7C%20ForEach-Object%20%7B%20Rename-Item%20%24_%20-NewName%20%22Prefix_%24_%22%20%7D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-21",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Sort-Object:** 按指定属性对对象进行排序"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-22",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-ChildItem | Sort-Object Length -Descending"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-23",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Format-Table:** 将输出格式化为带有指定列的表格"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-24",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Service | Format-Table -AutoSize  # ft alias"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-25",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**Format-List:** 将输出格式化为属性和值的列表"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-26",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "PowerShell",
      "code": "Get-Process | Format-List -Property Name, CPU  # fl alias"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-27",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F",
